sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server
    
    Client->>Server: 1. Login with credentials
    Server->>Server: 2. Verify credentials
    Server->>Server: 3. Generate JWT (Payload, Sign)
    Server-->>Client: 4. Return Token
    
    Note over Client: 5. Store in localStorage
    
    Client->>Server: 6. Request with Header {Authorization: Bearer ...}
    Server->>Server: 7. Verify Token (Sign, Expiry)
    Server->>Server: 8. Fetch User Context
    Server->>Server: 9. Process Request
    Server-->>Client: 10. Response